<p><b>Eric John Ernest Hobsbawm</b> <a href="/wiki/Companion_of_Honour" title="Companion of Honour" class="mw-redirect">CH</a>, FBA, (born <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1917-06-09"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="06-09"><a href="/wiki/June_9" title="June 9">June 9</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1917" title="1917">1917</a></span>) is a <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom">British</a> <a href="/wiki/Historical_materialism" title="Historical materialism">Marxist historian</a> and <a href="/wiki/Author" title="Author">author</a>.</p>
